import React from 'react';
import { Link } from 'react-router-dom';

import Box from '@mui/material/Box';
import Step from '@mui/material/Step';
import Typography from '@mui/material/Typography'
import Stepper from '@mui/material/Stepper';
import StepLabel from '@mui/material/StepLabel';

const CheckoutSteps = ({ step1, step2, step3, step4 }) => {
  return (
    <Box>
      <Stepper activeStep={-1}>
        <Step completed={step1}>
          <StepLabel>
            <Typography component={Link} style={{ color: 'white', textDecoration: 'none' }} to='/login'>
              Sign In
            </Typography>
          </StepLabel>
        </Step>
        <Step completed={step2}>
          <StepLabel>
            <Link style={{ color: 'white' }} to='/shipping'>
              Shipping
            </Link>
          </StepLabel>
        </Step>
        <Step completed={step3}>
          <StepLabel>
            <Link style={{ color: 'white' }} to='/payment'>
              Payment
            </Link>
          </StepLabel>
        </Step>
        <Step completed={step4}>
          <StepLabel>
            <Link style={{ color: 'white' }} to='/placeorder'>
              Place Order
            </Link>
          </StepLabel>
        </Step>
      </Stepper>
    </Box>
  );
};

export default CheckoutSteps;
